Hello <!channel>
There is a new project being launched to support Health Care Workers. We want to provide a bot service where we can address the immediate needs that the HCW are experiencing on a daily basis due to discrimination around the virus. We would like to have a kick-off meeting to brainstorm how to organize the service and the best way to address the more severe problems.

If you know about the problems or have recommendations about how to implement the solutions using our bot, please join the kick-off meeting at 3PM EST 10pm EAT today.
